      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. She runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those weekend getaways! It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is looking for a new owner who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin; you're going to love how it handles!",
