    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect if you're looking for something that runs smooth and looks great on the road. It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure! I've taken good care of it, so come on by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself. Can't wait to find it a new home!",
